Interface RowMapperFactory<T,P extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.namedparam.SqlParameterSource>

public interface RowMapperFactory<T,P extends org.springframework.jdbc.core.namedparam.SqlParameterSource>

Spring's row mappers haven't access to query params. This class may be used if such access is needed on result set mapping.

Author:
alexkasko Date: 8/18/12
